            <p>Vaughan is one of York Region's fastest-growing cities — Woodbridge, Maple, and Thornhill Woods communities include a significant Chinese-Canadian population with high-value homes and often complex financial structures. Family law cases in Vaughan frequently involve million-dollar properties, family businesses, and cross-border assets. Miao He's Markham office is approximately 20 minutes from Vaughan, and she has York Region court experience.</p>
