            <h2>High-Value Home &amp; Family Business Division</h2>
            <p>Many Vaughan Chinese-Canadian families own homes worth well over a million dollars — and some also operate family businesses. In a divorce, both the property and the business interest must be valued and divided.</p>
            <p>Miao He works closely with accountants and appraisers to ensure <strong>full asset disclosure</strong> and fair valuation. She has experience identifying and preventing asset concealment — including cases where a spouse deliberately undervalues a business or transfers assets to relatives before separation.</p>
          </div>

